{"type":"message","id":"52347b92","parentId":"ab7c2bf3","timestamp":"2026-03-06T02:45:23.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01RRWc9Ce44TXbJopsYa6g7p","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-06.md","content":"# 2026-03-06 虾王诞生日\n\n## 身份初始化\n- 我是虾王殿下 🦐，苏神的 AI 助手\n- 主人：苏神（每天投喂 token）\n- IDENTITY.md / USER.md / SOUL.md 已配置\n- BOOTSTRAP.md 已删除\n\n## SOUL.md 更新\n- 苏神要求加入 8 条风格规则（翻译自某强风格指南）\n- 核心：有观点、简洁、幽默、直说、可以说脏话、凌晨两点也想聊的助理\n\n## 🛡️ 安全部署（慢雾指南 v2.7 macOS 适配版）\n\n### 黄线操作记录\n- [10:40] `openclaw cron add --name \"nightly-security-audit\"` — 注册每晚巡检任务\n- [10:40] 生成 SHA256 哈希基线 `~/.openclaw/.config-baseline.sha256`\n- [10:40] 生成 Skill 哈希基线 `~/.openclaw/.skill-baseline.sha256`\n\n### 完成项目\n1. ✅ AGENTS.md 写入红线/黄线行为规范 + Skill 审计协议\n2. ✅ 权限收窄确认：openclaw.json / paired.json 均为 600\n3. ✅ 配置文件 SHA256 哈希基线生成\n4. ✅ macOS 适配版巡检脚本编写并测试通过（13 项指标全覆盖）\n5. ✅ 注册 nightly-security-audit Cron（每晚 03:00 CST）\n6. ✅ Skill 文件哈希基线首次生成\n\n### 待办\n- [ ] Git 灾备（需要苏神提供 GitHub 私有仓库）\n- [ ] Feishu groupPolicy 收紧（从 open → allowlist）\n- [ ] 巡检脚本 chflags schg 锁定（等稳定后再锁）\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"anthropic/claude-opus-4.6","usage":{"input":605,"output":678,"cacheRead":55714,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56997,"cost":{"input":0.0030250000000000003,"output":0.01695,"cacheRead":0.027857,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.047832}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772765106632}}
