{"type":"message","id":"1bc3792b","parentId":"ff81e7dc","timestamp":"2026-03-06T02:45:32.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定了苏神。总结一下完成了什么：\n\n**✅ 已部署**\n1. **红线/黄线行为规范** → 写入 AGENTS.md，macOS 适配\n2. **核心文件权限** → openclaw.json + paired.json 均 600 ✅\n3. **SHA256 哈希基线** → 配置文件 + Skill 文件双基线\n4. **13 项巡检脚本** → macOS 适配版，已测试通过\n5. **每晚 3:00 自动巡检** → Cron 已注册，下次运行明天凌晨 3 点\n6. **Skill/MCP 安装审计协议** → 写入 AGENTS.md\n\n**⏳ 后续可选**\n- **Git 灾备**：给我一个 GitHub 私有仓库地址就能配\n- **Feishu groupPolicy 收紧**：当前是 open，建议改 allowlist（这是 3 个 CRITICAL 告警的根源）\n- **巡检脚本锁定**：等跑几天稳定后用 `chflags schg` 锁死\n\nFeishu 那个 groupPolicy 要不要现在收紧？那是目前最大的安全隐患。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"anthropic/claude-opus-4.6","usage":{"input":795,"output":365,"cacheRead":56244,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57404,"cost":{"input":0.003975,"output":0.009125000000000001,"cacheRead":0.028121999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.041221999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772765123400}}
